This volume contains the papers selected for presentation at the 13th Workshop on Privacy in the Electronic Society (WPES 2014), held in Scottsdale, Arizona, USA, on November 3, 2014, in conjunction with the ACM Conference on Computer and Communications Security (ACM CCS). 
 
In response to the workshop's call for papers, 67 papers were submitted to the conference from 25 different countries. Each paper has been reviewed by three members of the program committee, who considered its significance, novelty, technical quality, and interest for the research and industy communities in their evaluation. The program committee's work was carried out electronically, yielding intensive discussion. Of the submitted papers, the program committee accepted 17 full papers and 9 short papers (an acceptance rate of 39%) for presentation at the workshop.